display_name.description:
User-friendly name that can be used in UI to display the namespace
name.

objects.description: One or more object definitions in the namespace.

namespace.description: A namespace name that is unique across all users.

visibility.description:
Namespace visibility. Valid value is public or private. Default is
private.

protected.description:
Namespace protection for deletion. Valid value is true or false.
Default is false.

resource_type_associations.description: One or more resource types that are associated with this namespace.

properties.description: One or more property definitions in the namespace.
